    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! It's been totally babied since day one, always garage-kept, and that paint is still gleaming. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership hassle, this is definitely the one. Come take it for a spin, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
