    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem for the discerning enthusiast. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear, still retaining that new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has a full, documented service history performed exclusively by certified technicians, ensuring the engine and transmission operate with surgical precision. This is not just a used car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive excellence. Included are all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom car cover. If you demand the best, this is your vehicle.",
      "price": 48900.0,
